  "content": "<p data-pid=\"xuM9coQl\">从记忆理论上来说：</p><p data-pid=\"dwT5yYI4\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/57020308\" class=\"internal\">间隔重复</a>+ <a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/57113246\" class=\"internal\">测试效应</a></p><p data-pid=\"v5SFy4rO\">两者结合效果很好，但是只是理论，以我刷知乎的个人经验，只有理论的回答几乎帮不上忙</p><p data-pid=\"8QleAfS6\">所以我就介绍一下可以半个小时内开始，并能坚持一年以上的实际操作方法：借助 Anki 来进行学习。</p><p data-pid=\"pZnE99bI\">先发几张使用过程中的图片</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1af7c2ed8d2a18aa49d96d4fb8526b2a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1062\" data-rawheight=\"602\" data-original-token=\"v2-ec139c3da7839ca1ddf771caeb5e91c5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e17ffca9d00f77f06dd335631fc4aba8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1062\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-1af7c2ed8d2a18aa49d96d4fb8526b2a_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1062&#39; height=&#39;602&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1062\" data-rawheight=\"602\" data-original-token=\"v2-ec139c3da7839ca1ddf771caeb5e91c5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e17ffca9d00f77f06dd335631fc4aba8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1062\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-1af7c2ed8d2a18aa49d96d4fb8526b2a_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1af7c2ed8d2a18aa49d96d4fb8526b2a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-29aae2ab2b316595b087b75bc7aac4b7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"908\" data-rawheight=\"549\" data-original-token=\"v2-ec953bf9bc7154c4ede106181c22d855\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4b1d46043088664e5ec97a1b37144230_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"908\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-29aae2ab2b316595b087b75bc7aac4b7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;908&#39; height=&#39;549&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"908\" data-rawheight=\"549\" data-original-token=\"v2-ec953bf9bc7154c4ede106181c22d855\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4b1d46043088664e5ec97a1b37144230_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"908\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-29aae2ab2b316595b087b75bc7aac4b7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-29aae2ab2b316595b087b75bc7aac4b7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e7ad740624dfbd49014261a378e5255c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"634\" data-rawheight=\"542\" data-original-token=\"v2-b7bc9d68cc3bad4191d13f9c9ee9231d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9a641a697f7c377f601ead979040ecf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"634\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e7ad740624dfbd49014261a378e5255c_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;634&#39; height=&#39;542&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"634\" data-rawheight=\"542\" data-original-token=\"v2-b7bc9d68cc3bad4191d13f9c9ee9231d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9a641a697f7c377f601ead979040ecf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"634\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e7ad740624dfbd49014261a378e5255c_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e7ad740624dfbd49014261a378e5255c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2eb3267a69879acc88634e8c4e328d33_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1062\" data-rawheight=\"602\" data-original-token=\"v2-f9323db737b41fcc19b188f0c976e404\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-0eee92339a7283de0f0f007089e9242c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1062\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2eb3267a69879acc88634e8c4e328d33_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1062&#39; height=&#39;602&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1062\" data-rawheight=\"602\" data-original-token=\"v2-f9323db737b41fcc19b188f0c976e404\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-0eee92339a7283de0f0f007089e9242c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1062\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2eb3267a69879acc88634e8c4e328d33_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2eb3267a69879acc88634e8c4e328d33_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"FQ5Y6hPe\">简单介绍：Anki 是一款有<b>记忆</b>辅助算法的<b>笔记</b>软件，支持常见的 windows、mac、linux、安卓和 ios 系统。</p><p data-pid=\"y8wy4Rdk\">快速入门方式：</p><p data-pid=\"Z9w-0pWQ\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Anki 备战高考手册 · 看云</a> </p><p data-pid=\"leisVYez\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Ankidroid (Anki 安卓版) 基本使用教程</a> </p><p data-pid=\"pACMKtKf\">笔记获取：</p><p data-pid=\"LNvFdHDq\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/40144454\" class=\"internal\">2698张体验卡片，带每一位高中生进入Anki学习法的世界</a></p><p data-pid=\"k7OurTdO\">最后，说一些自己踩过的坑：</p><p data-pid=\"YbkO4gV3\">千万不要看太多学习方法，实践为主。以及，没有给出理论和实际相结合的学习方法，哪怕再科学与正确，也没有多大用处，反而会给人带来一种感觉良好。</p><p data-pid=\"eiigJuq0\">最后，给一下我自己高考前的学习统计数据：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f574c9463a44f5ccd3d3bc54c7b23b86_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1665\" data-rawheight=\"3420\" data-original-token=\"v2-ee60d0c21d662c8b5e6f9ede92671e3c\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-60e193b770b8465db4e684d76dbb16d5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1665\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f574c9463a44f5ccd3d3bc54c7b23b86_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1665&#39; height=&#39;3420&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1665\" data-rawheight=\"3420\" data-original-token=\"v2-ee60d0c21d662c8b5e6f9ede92671e3c\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-60e193b770b8465db4e684d76dbb16d5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1665\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f574c9463a44f5ccd3d3bc54c7b23b86_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f574c9463a44f5ccd3d3bc54c7b23b86_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"CPL3-1La\">不妨抽帮个小时，少看几篇理论，多实践一个方法。</p>",
